    <section name="Request parameters loader valve">
      <subsection name="Description">
        <p>
        The pipeline processing valve that read the parameters from request parameters and 
        from parsed url path and store it as a parameters container in thread context.
        The parameters stays available throughout the pipeline processing. To access use
        <a href="../apidocs/org/objectledge/parameters/RequestParameters.html#getRequestParameters(org.objectledge.context.Context)">getRequestParametes(Context)</a> method
         </p>
